******* "Operators"

1: Arthmatic Operators 

* Binary 

Addition (+)
subtraction (-)
multiplication (*)
divison (/)
modulo (%)

* Unary 


Increment (++)
Decrement (--)



1: Post (a++) = Use & Then Update 
2: pre (++a) = Update & Then Use



2: Assignment Operator/Compound Assignment 

 =  : a = 10
 += : a =a+5 = a+5 
 -= : a = a-5 = a-=2
 *= :  a = a*5 = a*=2
 /= :  a = a/5 = a/=2
 
 
 
 3:  Relational Operators 
 
